            "text": "<p></p><ol><li><strong>White Saree with Red Floral Embroidery</strong>: In a scene resonating with nostalgia, Fatima dons a white saree adorned with delicate red floral motifs. Paired with silver bangles and deep red lipstick, this ensemble exudes vintage charm, reminiscent of classic Bengali cinema.<br/><br/><br/></li><li><strong>Teal Blue Saree</strong>: Amidst the bustling streets, Fatima's teal blue saree brings a sense of calm and grace. The printed blouse and flowing hair add to the ensemble's contemporary appeal, making it suitable for both casual outings and festive occasions.<br/><br/><br/></li><li><strong>Printed Saree with Red Borders</strong>: During a romantic sequence with R. Madhavan, Fatima wears a printed saree featuring red borders. This choice adds a touch of vibrancy and warmth, enhancing the scene's emotional depth.</li></ol>",
